description:
In this Everything Iconic POP Dive, Danny takes a break from talking Bravo and reality TV to welcome original GLEE star and Broadway performer Jenna Ushkowitz (co-host of the Showmance podcast).They discuss all things Glee-- performing for President Obama and Queen Oprah, on-set turmoil, reboot possibilities, self-care, and more!


*To support this pod & access bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
